headline: Aristotle Capital Value Equity Strategy Chose to Exit Millrose Properties (MRP)
summary: Aristotle Capital Management, LLC, an investment management company, released its “Value Equity Strategy” first quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here.
